Package: MarginalCausality
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Solution to the Marginal Causality
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Gilles Monneret
Maintainer: Gilles Monneret <gilles.monneret@upmc.fr>
Description: Under the framework of linear gaussian acyclic graph without latent variable, and with both observational and interventional datas,
    this package answer the question of causality between the interventional node and some other node.
    To do so, we use a bayes factor which is computed by this package.
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: testthat, mvtnorm, stats,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown, igraph, Rgraphviz
VignetteBuilder: knitr
